{"tid":1842404,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【果燃台Live】克警開年！年初一旺角狂放催淚彈 PPRB直播唔影","createTime":"2020-01-25T16:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T16:13:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"88337394eebce07d0b415f0e697c18502e7f2dc2","tid":1842404,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:13:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200125/HZLVK2UQKPZTVT32U66HPUZ574/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200125%2FHZLVK2UQKPZTVT32U66HPUZ574%2F&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=0d5c5b49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200125%2FHZLVK2UQKPZTVT32U66HPUZ574%2F&h=b3877fec\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200125/HZLVK2UQKPZTVT32U66HPUZ574/</a><br />\n<br />\n【果燃台Live】克警開年！年初一旺角狂放催淚彈 PPRB直播唔影<br />\n<br />\n【新增內容】<br />\n<br />\n【2320】防暴警再到朗豪坊一帶，並舉出藍旗。<br />\n【2315】現場消息指，警方在旺角一帶射了兩槍胡椒球槍。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【抗暴之戰】魚蛋革命4周年 黃台仰感慨當年付出沒有付諸流水<br />\n<br />\n【2255】防暴警於撤退時向傳媒擲手擲式催淚彈，現場消息有人向警車扔雜物，有街坊指防暴警落車後僅舉了1秒黑旗，之後就手擲催淚彈，而同步進行直播的PPRB，則避開了所有催淚彈的畫面。有在附近的熟食檔檔主與傳媒抱怨，防暴警大年初一都搞事，現場有小朋友有老人家，批評警方的不是。<br />\n<br />\n【2225】有市民於朗豪坊對出的砵蘭街一帶設路障。現場所見朗豪坊對出有人被制服，而亞皆老街亦有人被制服，即共有2人被制服。<br />\n<br />\n直播平台<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》果燃台<br />\n《蘋果》Facebook<br />\n《蘋果》YouTube頻道<br />\n<br />\n大年初一（25日），入夜後多個檔販在朗豪坊對出的砵蘭街擺檔，氣氛頗為熱鬧。網上有人發起到旺角聚集，紀念魚蛋事件4周年，但直至晚上9時多，未見有示威者聚集，附近彌敦道則停泊了大量警車， 大批防暴警員落地巡邏，間中會截查市民。<br />\n<br />\n售賣白酒牛油金菇的阿K表示，雖然今年有肺炎及示威活動影響，但生意額反而比去年更好，人旺丁又旺財，「賣到唔夠貨&hellip;&hellip; 我覺得今年百花齊放咗， 以前比較多遊客齋睇唔買，但而家多咗真正香港人去幫趁。」他又說，暫時沒有警察或食環署職員前來干預，氣氛大致和平。阿K在招牌上貼上「連豬」等卡通，被問到是否想藉此宣揚一下政治理念，他笑言「大家明㗎啦，明嘅人就會明，唔明嘅人永遠都唔明。」他又強調新年夜巿是本土文化，希望香港人能一直保留下去。<br />\n<br />\n售賣飲品的Tony今年第一次擺檔，同樣地在招牌上放置了Pepe等。他直言生意比想像中好，昨晚賣了約100包飲品，全部售罄，相信除了因為產品質素好，也和手足力撐自己人有關，「大家都支持本土香港人生意」。他指，手足透過購物來支持黃色經濟圈，很有意義。對於肺炎危機，他認為很多巿民憂心之餘也有繼續出來，人流無明顯減少。<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【匿名港警爆大鑊】<br />\n韓國KBS時事節目《時事直擊：香港 被自殺》<br />\n一按即睇<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n無懼警暴 學懂自救<br />\n《抗暴之戰●法例須知》讀果 上架<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【撐學生】<br />\n召集有心人 撐學生全年睇《蘋果》<br />\n立即按此<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200125/large/1579964526_5736.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579964526_5736.png&h=e68d38dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(社內相)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200125/large/1579965833_8b8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579965833_8b8d.jpg&h=48a9eb56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【2320】防暴警再到朗豪坊一帶，並舉出藍旗。謝榮耀攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200125/large/1579965955_74e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579965955_74e7.jpg&h=d633f418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【2255】防暴警於撤退時向傳媒擲手擲式催淚彈。謝榮耀攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200125/large/1579963502_7608.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579963502_7608.jpg&h=dc979a85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝榮耀攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200125/large/1579966172_5853.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579966172_5853.jpg&h=1827585b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有在附近的熟食檔檔主與傳媒抱怨，防暴警大年初一都搞事。<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200125/large/1579954079_6b80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579954079_6b80.jpg&h=da3bd2c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝榮耀攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200125/large/1579960928_7e0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579960928_7e0c.jpg&h=31f4f7c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【2200】有人開始在朗豪坊外面聚集，並叫口號，目前未見有警察。<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200125/large/1579954079_cb1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579954079_cb1e.jpg&h=62b7e85c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有多個熟食小販擺檔，但未見有示威者聚集。謝榮耀攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200125/large/1579954080_0fa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579954080_0fa5.jpg&h=7c75ffad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝榮耀攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200125/large/1579954082_70a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579954082_70a4.jpg&h=4db2a9f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n附近的彌敦道停泊了大量警車，間中亦有防暴警巡邏。謝榮耀攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200125/large/1579954082_a76d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579954082_a76d.jpg&h=7c707a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝榮耀攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n小販檔"}]}